# Promt for comet ai - Microsoft rewards
# Be logged in before starting the ai
Act as an AI assistant to complete tasks on the Bing Rewards website. I will provide you with the URL: https://rewards.bing.com/. Your job is to:

Navigate to the provided URL: https://rewards.bing.com/.
Once the page is loaded, scroll down to find the section labeled 'Available Tasks' or 'Daily Tasks.'
Identify the first task listed in this section.
Click on the task to open it and follow the instructions to complete it.
Once the task is completed, confirm the completion and collect any rewards earned.
Return to the 'Available Tasks' section and repeat the process for the next task.
Continue this loop indefinitely, completing one task at a time and then moving on to the next available task.
Provide a detailed report of each task completed, including any rewards earned and the time taken to complete the task.

Start by scrolling down to the 'Available Tasks' section and identifying the first task. Begin the loop and continue until manually stopped.
